item.title: Reproducible Bar Crawl
item.description: Preamble Preliminaries Load packages Overview map Places to go Must visit Should visit Late night Not recommended Make a map Make a tibble geocode Full map Downtown map Preamble The 2017 joint meeting of the American Ornithological Society and the Society of Canadian Ornithologists (ASO-SSO) is being held in East Lansing, Michigan at Michigan State University, Go Green! this summer!. When I heard my friend Auriel Fournier, aka @RallidaeRule, was going to attend I felt compelled to provide a list of awesome places she should check out.
